<%- include('partials/header') -%>

<main class="container text-tertiary d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div>
        <header class="text-center py-5">
            <h1 class="display-4">Our Story</h1>
            <p class="lead">Connecting people through food, conversation, and shared experiences.</p>
          </header>
        <img class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block rounded"src="/imgs/about.webp" alt="About Image" style="width: 100%; max-width: 1080px;">
          <div class="container my-5">
            <section>
              <h2 class="h3">How Foodship Was Born</h2>
              <p>Foodship was created with one simple mission in mind: to bring people together over food and meaningful conversation. Born out of a passion for connecting people, Roosiel Agramonte, the creator of Foodship, realized that dining out with strangers could be an exciting way to learn about new cultures, ideas, and perspectives. That was the spark that led to the idea for this app.</p>
            </section>
        
            <section class="mt-4">
              <h2 class="h3">The Vision</h2>
              <p>Foodship isn't just about food—it's about creating spaces where people can bond, chat, and share experiences while enjoying a meal. Whether you're looking for a place to talk about tech, art, or just life in general, Foodship matches you with others who share similar interests. It’s all about fostering connections, one meal at a time.</p>
            </section>
        
            <section class="mt-4">
              <h2 class="h3">What’s Next?</h2>
              <p>Since its launch, Foodship has been growing steadily, helping more and more people connect over shared meals. The team (currently a one-person show!) is dedicated to enhancing the user experience, optimizing the app, and expanding the community. There’s always more on the horizon, so stay tuned!</p>
            </section>
        
            <section class="mt-4 text-center">
              <h2 class="h4">Join Us on Our Journey</h2>
              <p><a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Join Foodship Now</a> and connect with new people over a meal!</p>
            </section>
        
          </div>

    </div>

</main>

